'''克丽斯廷·胡松'''（{{lang-de|Christin Hussong}}，{{bd|1994年|3月17日||}}）是一名参加[[标枪|标枪]]的德国[[田径|田径]]运动员。她曾在2018年欧洲田径锦标赛女子标枪项目上以67米90的破锦标赛纪录的成绩夺得冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/en/germanys-christin-hussong-sets-javelin-record-at-european-championships/a-45042932|title=Germany's Christin Hussong sets javelin record at European Championships|publisher=Deutsche Welle|date=2018-08-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180811000021/https://www.dw.com/en/germanys-christin-hussong-sets-javelin-record-at-european-championships/a-45042932|archivedate=2018-08-11|accessdate=2020-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她是LAZ Zweibrücken田径队的成员，她的教练是其父亲乌多·胡松。<ref name="laz">{{cite web |url=http://www.laz.de/athleten/christin-hussong |title=Christin Hussong |publisher=LAZ Zweibrücken |accessdate=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508061423/http://www.laz.de/athleten/christin-hussong |archive-date=2019-05-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pfaelzischer-merkur.de/titelseite/aufmacher/Aufmacher-Zweibruecken-Speerwurf;art27803,4865227 |date=2013-07-18 |accessdate=2015-07-22 |author=Kissel, Svenja |title=LAZ-Speerwerferin Christin Hussong startet bei der U20-EM in Rieti |publisher=Pfälzischer Merkur |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723043718/http://www.pfaelzischer-merkur.de/titelseite/aufmacher/Aufmacher-Zweibruecken-Speerwurf;art27803,4865227 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

